WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.329 --> 00:00:05.799
HERE'S A FUN GAME: Count how many times I
say BOOBS in the next 2 minutes!

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:12.590
Hey everyone, Laci Green here for DNews.

00:00:12.590 --> 00:00:13.680
It's time for a heart to heart.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:17.390
There are a lot of things that make it hard
to exercise, and something that's definitely

00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:18.540
on that list?

00:00:18.540 --> 00:00:19.540
BOOOOOBS.

00:00:19.540 --> 00:00:20.540
Oh yeah.

00:00:20.540 --> 00:00:23.000
I'm no stranger to the boob struggle, it's
a real life issue.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.480
Recently, a study published in the Journal
of Physical Activity and Health finds that

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:28.440
I am by NO MEANS alone.

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:33.100
In fact, boobs are a barrier to exercise for
nearly 1 in 5 women, or 17%.

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:36.700
They also found that women with boobs of all
sizes report this problem.

00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:41.150
It's the first study to examine the unique
role that boobs play in women's participation

00:00:41.150 --> 00:00:42.270
in sports.

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:44.000
Boobs were the 4th most common barrier cited.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.960
#1 is a lack of energy, #2 is time constraints,
and #3 is health limitations.

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:52.451
The main complaints were that they weren't
able to find a proper sports bra and that

00:00:52.451 --> 00:00:53.980
they felt embarrassed.

00:00:53.980 --> 00:00:58.010
Which actually really surprises me - I would
have thought it would have been ACHEY, SHARP,

00:00:58.010 --> 00:01:02.611
AGONIZING PAIN.....but maybe that's what they
mean by "can't find a proper sports bra".

00:01:02.611 --> 00:01:07.350
Bra fit is a biggie - without a good sports
bra, high impact exercise is ALL KINDS of

00:01:07.350 --> 00:01:08.350
uncomfortable.

00:01:08.350 --> 00:01:12.750
A poorly fitted bra is one that allows excess
tension on the Coopers Ligaments, which stretches

00:01:12.750 --> 00:01:14.551
and strains your breast's natural support
system.

00:01:14.551 --> 00:01:18.920
This pulling results in both immediate and
lasting pain.

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:20.740
Plus it allows chafing!

00:01:20.740 --> 00:01:25.040
I have scars from chafing so badly on a run
that I started to bleed.

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.460
Cute, I know.

00:01:26.460 --> 00:01:31.170
But making exercise more comfortable for the
girls goes beyond a good bra -- it means confronting

00:01:31.170 --> 00:01:34.230
the embarrassment that we feel about our bodies
and the way they move.

00:01:34.230 --> 00:01:37.130
For me, this was just a HUUUUGE deterrent
when I was young.

00:01:37.130 --> 00:01:41.480
I was also really upset by the way that guys
ogled at me in gym class or on the street,

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:43.590
sometimes even shouting explicit comments
about my chest.

00:01:43.590 --> 00:01:44.940
I didn't want their attention - I just wanted
to exercise.

00:01:44.940 --> 00:01:50.840
So, for all my boobly friends out there: TRANSCEND
THE BOOBLINESS.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:55.700
Don't let your boobs inhibit you(!) - whether
by way of sports bras or insecurity or terrible

00:01:55.700 --> 00:01:56.820
people you'll come across.

00:01:56.820 --> 00:02:00.600
Save up, have a proper fitting, and invest
in a good bra.

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:03.370
Or as I like to call it: my slingshot.

00:02:03.370 --> 00:02:05.090
It's something you deserve!

00:02:05.090 --> 00:02:07.590
As for that embarrassment, it helps me to
remember that boobs are: boobs!

00:02:07.590 --> 00:02:08.590
Deep, I know.

00:02:08.590 --> 00:02:09.590
But really: they're part of being female.

00:02:09.590 --> 00:02:10.590
That's a biological fact.

00:02:10.590 --> 00:02:12.280
I mean, we all have them to one degree or
another -- sometimes to a really great degree--

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:14.800
and they're nothing to be ashamed of.

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:18.830
If anything, the world should be ashamed for
making others feel bad about their body parts

00:02:18.830 --> 00:02:19.830
and for being disrespectful.

00:02:19.830 --> 00:02:20.830
So....the world should like....stop that.

00:02:20.830 --> 00:02:21.830
Asap.

00:02:21.830 --> 00:02:22.940
Thanks for joining me for DNews everyone,
we'll see you next time. ;)

